Lagerstein - Drink Til We Die  mp3  320k    2014  .....
Lagerstein are a folking, drinking, shouting and pirating rock/metal outfit. "Drink 'Til We Die" is loaded with 12 fun filled tracks of loud guitars, soaring keytars, earworm melodies and adventurous tales that will have you singing drunken sea shanties for drinks and drinks.

Lagerstein's debut album, Drink 'Til We Die, was launched on Sunday the 19th of August 2011.

Current Members:


  - The Immobilizer: Bass (2010-present)

  - The Majestic Beast: Guitars (lead) (2010-present)

  - Neil Rummy Rackers: Guitars (rhythm) (2010-present)

  - Mother Junkst: Keytar, Violin (2010-present)

  - Oldmate Dazzle: Drums (2011-present)

  - Jacob, The Fiercest Pirate in all the Caribbean: Keyboards (2013-present)

  - Captain Gregaaarrr: Vocals (2013-present)
